2012-08-31

    o	Use resolved native symbols.

2010-02-17

    o	Added CT n-gram counting.
    o	We now use vectors instead of pairlists to avoid memory
	corruption problems.

2010-01-09

    o	Use perl in word splitting in textcnt. This fixes a problem
	with combining characters when using the default split
	pattern.

